OL,3,CSerial rapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cabusing vulnerable girls
OL,6,FA serial rapist has been given a life
OL,7,Fsentence by Jersey's Royal Court.
OL,9,FShay John Edward Bester, 50, faced
OL,10,Fmultiple counts of assaulting and
OL,11,Fraping three vulnerable teenage girls,
OL,12,Fone of whom was underage.
OL,14,FThe sentence will see Bester serve a
OL,15,Fminimum of 15 years behind bars, with
OL,16,Fthe judge saying this is necessary as
OL,17,Fhe could still be a serious risk to
OL,18,Fthe public.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
