CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776885105
OL,3,CSerial rapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cabusing vulnerable girls
OL,6,FBester is already in prison for
OL,7,Ftrafficking, rape and other offences
OL,8,Fagainst another victim, for which he
OL,9,Fwas convicted in 2023.
OL,11,FIn this separate case, Bester's
OL,12,Foffences against the first of the
OL,13,Fthree victims began in 1994 - when she
OL,14,Fwas a teenager.
OL,16,FThe Royal Court heard how he gained
OL,17,Fher trust, and then became
OL,18,Fmanipulative and controlling.
OL,20,FThis was a pattern that continued with
OL,21,Fhis other two victims.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
