PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776885105
OL,3,CSerial rapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cabusing vulnerable girls
OL,6,FBester raped and assaulted them, and
OL,7,Fisolated them from support networks.
OL,9,FThey were already particularly
OL,10,Fvulnerable - and he made them wholly
OL,11,Freliant on him - using drugs and
OL,12,Falcohol as part of his control.
OL,14,FAll of his victims have been left with
OL,15,Fpost-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD)
OL,16,F- their impact statements in court
OL,17,Fdescribed flashbacks, panic attacks
OL,18,Fand struggling to trust others.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776885105
OL,3,CSerial rapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cabusing vulnerable girls
OL,6,FOne of the victim's testimonies
OL,7,Fdescribed how Bester had taken
OL,8,Fadvantage of her vulnerable situation.
OL,10,FShe explained: "I was scared ... I had
OL,11,Fno contact with my family or education.
OL,13,F"I was all alone ... he made me feel
OL,14,Flike he would protect me, almost like
OL,15,Fa parent figure.
OL,17,F"He took advantage of this."
OL,19,FIn her statement, the victim went on
OL,20,Fto describe the long-term damage
OL,21,FBester's abuse had inflicted upon her.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776885105
OL,3,CSerial rapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cabusing vulnerable girls
OL,6,FShe added: "I suffered so much trauma,
OL,7,FI struggle to function as a normal
OL,8,Fperson.
OL,10,F"I moved away from St Helier so I
OL,11,Fdidn't have to see him. I still get
OL,12,Fscared when walking through the town,
OL,13,FI see his face on random men. I still
OL,14,Ffeel a very real threat, even though I
OL,15,Fknow he can't get to me.
OL,17,F"I still blame myself. I can't shift
OL,18,Fthe guilt. I want him to know the
OL,19,Fimpact he's had on me."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
