PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776885105
OL,3,CSerial rapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cabusing vulnerable girls
OL,6,FThe three victims in this trial came
OL,7,Fforward separately, and their cases
OL,8,Fbecame linked when Jersey Police
OL,9,Frecognised similarities with Bester's
OL,10,F2023 conviction.
OL,12,FDC Eliane Jones, told ITV News: "The
OL,13,Fnature of the case is naturally very
OL,14,Fdistressing. The crimes he committed
OL,15,Fagainst the three vulnerable victim
OL,16,Fwere abhorrent.
OL,18,F"The conclusion of today just
OL,19,Fhighlights that it's never too late to
OL,20,Fcome forward, no matter when offences
OL,21,Ftook place.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
