OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776885105
OL,3,CSerial rapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cabusing vulnerable girls
OL,6,F"Credit should be given to the three
OL,7,Fvictims who came forward all this time
OL,8,Flater."
OL,10,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,11,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,12,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,13,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,14,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,15,Fbelow...
